message.content:
Here is a sample healthy meal plan for you:

Breakfast:

* 2 whole eggs, cooked with spinach and feta cheese
* 1 slice of whole grain toast
* 1/2 avocado, sliced
* 1/2 cup of mixed berries

Snack:

* 1 small apple
* 1 tablespoon of almond butter

Lunch:

* Grilled chicken breast with roasted vegetables (such as broccoli, carrots, and brussels sprouts) and a side salad with mixed greens and a light vinaigrette dressing

Snack:

* 1 small pear
* 1 ounce of cheddar cheese

Dinner:

* Grilled salmon with roasted asparagus and a side of brown rice

This meal plan includes a variety of protein sources, healthy fats, and complex carbohydrates to keep you full and satisfied. It also includes plenty of vegetables for added nutrients and fiber. Of course, feel free to customize the plan based on your individual needs and preferences!
